The Promotion will consist of six (6) months of free payroll services to Eligible Clients. An “Eligible Client” is a client that: (1) is not currently receiving payroll services from Paychex; (2) elects either the Paychex Flex® Pro, Select, Enterprise or Express payroll services package by entering into a service agreement with Paychex; (3) has between 1–49 employees at the time it commences payroll services; (4) processes its first payroll, on or before 3/19/26, with Paychex during the Promotion Period; and (5) continues to process payroll with Paychex for twelve (12) consecutive months. Paychex will credit an Eligible Client’s invoice for free payroll services in months four (4), five (5), six (6), seven (7), eight (8) and nine (9) following commencement of payroll processing services. An Eligible Client must be processing payroll with Paychex in order to receive six months of free payroll services, and any unused month is not redeemable in U.S. currency or for any other entity. The Promotion only applies to payroll services, and Eligible Clients will be solely responsible for all fees due for services other than payroll services. The Promotion cannot be combined with any other offer and is a limited time offer that is only available during the Promotion Period. conversation.speaker: Seller
conversation.message: Hi, my name is Alex and I'm a Sales Development Representative at DeepData AI. I came across your company while researching innovative businesses in the industry, and I was impressed by your use of Paychex for payroll and HR solutions. Can you tell me a little bit about your current data processing workflow and how you're managing your HR and payroll data?

conversation.speaker: Buyer
conversation.message: (skeptical) Ah, another sales call. What makes you think we need your solution, Alex? We're already using Paychex for our payroll and HR needs, and it's been working fine for us so far.

conversation.speaker: Seller
conversation.message: I completely understand your skepticism, but that's exactly why I'm calling. While Paychex is a great solution for payroll and HR, our solution, DeepData AI, can help you unlock the full potential of your data by providing advanced analytics and insights. With our AI-powered data processing solution, you can automate tedious tasks, identify trends, and make data-driven decisions to drive business growth. For example, we've helped similar companies like yours reduce their data processing time by up to 50% and improve their decision-making by providing real-time insights.

conversation.speaker: Buyer
conversation.message: (still skeptical) I'm not sure I see the value in that. We're a small team, and we don't have a lot of complex data to process. Plus, we're already getting the analytics we need from Paychex. What makes your solution so special that it's worth considering?

conversation.speaker: Seller
conversation.message: I understand that you might not see the immediate value, but let me ask you, are you using your data to inform business decisions, or is it just sitting in a spreadsheet somewhere? DeepData AI can help you uncover hidden insights and opportunities that you might not be aware of. For instance, our solution can help you identify areas where you can optimize your payroll processing, reduce costs, and improve employee satisfaction. We've had clients who've used our solution to identify trends in employee turnover and make data-driven decisions to improve their retention rates. Would you be open to a quick demo to see how our solution can help you achieve your business goals?

conversation.speaker: Buyer
conversation.message: (somewhat interested) Okay, fine. I'll take a look. But make it quick and to the point. I don't have a lot of time to spare. And be honest with me, what's the cost of this solution, and how does it integrate with Paychex?

conversation.speaker: Seller
conversation.message: Absolutely, I'd be happy to provide a quick demo and answer any questions you may have. Our solution integrates seamlessly with Paychex, and we've had many clients who've successfully integrated our solution with their existing payroll and HR systems. As for the cost, it's competitive with other data processing solutions on the market, and we offer flexible pricing plans to fit your business needs. I can provide you with a custom quote after the demo, and we can discuss the details of the integration and implementation process. Would you like to schedule a demo for this week or next?
